    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/b064bfed3b968a20c1a64184187aaf8f.poster.avif?t=1699899924\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/b064bfed3b968a20c1a64184187aaf8f.webm?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/b064bfed3b968a20c1a64184187aaf8f.mp4?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NOIR STORM 是...</h2>一款美丽的叙事单击冒险游戏，灵感源自黑色电影，真实的历史，90年代的经典冒险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情:</h2>你将与丹尼尔·利昂（1952年布宜诺斯艾利斯市的私人调查员）并肩作战。他的搭档马丁内斯已经失踪多日。丹尼尔也差点儿因追查手中的唯一线索而遭受谋杀，他即将发现马丁内斯所牵连的事情远远超过了他的能力和掌控。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >情景设定：</h2>在50年代典型的音乐和视觉背景下，解决经典冒险游戏的挑战。使用丹尼尔的笔记本收集各类线索，追查每条线索，找到他危险的冒险的终点。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/193fab23340257864f083a9436dd5146.poster.avif?t=1699899924\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/193fab23340257864f083a9436dd5146.webm?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/193fab23340257864f083a9436dd5146.mp4?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/e3dc7086d0780cd14e035a3e607358c0.poster.avif?t=1699899924\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/e3dc7086d0780cd14e035a3e607358c0.webm?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/e3dc7086d0780cd14e035a3e607358c0.mp4?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/ab6b1032678fc14bc6a656725aa2affe.poster.avif?t=1699899924\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/ab6b1032678fc14bc6a656725aa2affe.webm?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/ab6b1032678fc14bc6a656725aa2affe.mp4?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>灵感源自黑色电影的经典单击冒险游戏。<br></li><li>故事叙述基于真实地点、角色、历史调查和真实战争元素。<br></li><li>通过对话、物品收集、解决难题以及使用笔记本电脑结合线索和数据推进调查，从而深入地了解各个角色。<br></li><li>像素艺术和动画伴随着独特的漫画插图。<br></li><li>了解南美洲纳粹的最终结局（基于著名阿根廷新闻工作者兼作家阿贝尔·巴斯蒂的真实调查）<br></li><li>雨，到处都是雨! 这毕竟是一场暴风雨......</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/fd2fe24894b395eae03dbf5227a9ecfc.poster.avif?t=1699899924\" width=598 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/fd2fe24894b395eae03dbf5227a9ecfc.webm?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/fd2fe24894b395eae03dbf5227a9ecfc.mp4?t=1699899924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845980/extras/678245e2d1c946ca6315aa15971b1fb3.poster.avif?t=1699899924\" width=59